- Actions: add supplier, edit, delete.
- Forms: supplier name/contact fields, phone/email/address/business metadata.
- States: branch-required error when no shop exists, success message, empty table.
- Mobile notes: Make branch selector sticky; supplier details should be a bottom sheet/card.

